00:00:08.330 --> 00:00:14.220 align:middle line:90%


00:00:14.220 --> 00:00:17.629 align:middle line:84%
>> I'm Uri Geller,
and this is my Legacy.

00:00:17.629 --> 00:00:21.122 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:21.122 --> 00:00:35.100 align:middle line:90%


00:00:35.100 --> 00:00:38.310 align:middle line:10%
I would describe
myself, Uri Geller,

00:00:38.310 --> 00:00:40.920 align:middle line:10%
as a person that
actually shocked

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:48.870 align:middle line:10%
the world with something
quite trivial and surprising.

00:00:48.870 --> 00:00:54.960 align:middle line:84%
You see, I always say
that the secret of success

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:57.510 align:middle line:90%
is originality.

00:00:57.510 --> 00:01:01.140 align:middle line:84%
And I came up with something
original, something

00:01:01.140 --> 00:01:04.120 align:middle line:90%
that was never seen before.

00:01:04.120 --> 00:01:09.200 align:middle line:84%
So I really shocked the
world with that feat.

00:01:09.200 --> 00:01:15.290 align:middle line:84%
I look at myself as someone,
maybe a freak of nature,

00:01:15.290 --> 00:01:22.100 align:middle line:84%
maybe a little advanced,
ahead of my time,

00:01:22.100 --> 00:01:25.655 align:middle line:84%
maybe something that
triggered my mind power.

00:01:25.655 --> 00:01:29.730 align:middle line:90%


00:01:29.730 --> 00:01:34.500 align:middle line:84%
My mental abilities began
at a very early age.

00:01:34.500 --> 00:01:37.520 align:middle line:10%
First of all, very
few people know this,

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:43.800 align:middle line:10%
but when I was about a year
old, my mother put me in a pram

00:01:43.800 --> 00:01:45.120 align:middle line:10%
under a window.

00:01:45.120 --> 00:01:47.910 align:middle line:84%
At that time in Israel,
it was Palestine,

00:01:47.910 --> 00:01:53.730 align:middle line:84%
and the British were the
rulers in Israel, in Palestine.

00:01:53.730 --> 00:01:58.890 align:middle line:84%
And a British soldier shot
two bullets into our window

00:01:58.890 --> 00:02:01.480 align:middle line:84%
from across the
railroad station.

00:02:01.480 --> 00:02:03.780 align:middle line:90%
And I remember that.

00:02:03.780 --> 00:02:09.479 align:middle line:84%
I remember the glass
shattering, falling slow motion

00:02:09.479 --> 00:02:10.530 align:middle line:90%
onto my face.

00:02:10.530 --> 00:02:13.305 align:middle line:84%
There was a little Teddy
bear that covered my face,

00:02:13.305 --> 00:02:14.430 align:middle line:90%
and nothing happened to me.

00:02:14.430 --> 00:02:16.620 align:middle line:90%
I wasn't even scratched.

00:02:16.620 --> 00:02:19.920 align:middle line:90%
So maybe that was a shock.

00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:23.490 align:middle line:84%
Maybe that was the
actual trigger.

00:02:23.490 --> 00:02:26.250 align:middle line:10%
The second experience
that happened to me

00:02:26.250 --> 00:02:32.250 align:middle line:10%
that definitely falls into
the category of a shock

00:02:32.250 --> 00:02:34.190 align:middle line:10%
is the following.

00:02:34.190 --> 00:02:38.140 align:middle line:90%
I'm about five years old.

00:02:38.140 --> 00:02:42.900 align:middle line:84%
I'm playing in an Arabic
garden, magical garden.

00:02:42.900 --> 00:02:45.060 align:middle line:90%
And I heard kittens cry.

00:02:45.060 --> 00:02:48.840 align:middle line:84%
And as a five-year-old,
I'm looking for them.

00:02:48.840 --> 00:02:57.600 align:middle line:84%
Suddenly, out of nowhere, I
see a huge sphere of light.

00:02:57.600 --> 00:02:59.550 align:middle line:90%
It's throbbing.

00:02:59.550 --> 00:03:02.110 align:middle line:84%
It's almost like
a living entity,

00:03:02.110 --> 00:03:07.230 align:middle line:84%
but it was just a
sphere, a ball of fire.

00:03:07.230 --> 00:03:11.880 align:middle line:84%
I look at this
phenomena, and then I

00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:15.780 align:middle line:84%
can see with my eyes
a beam, almost--

00:03:15.780 --> 00:03:18.450 align:middle line:84%
I describe it today
as a laser beam.

00:03:18.450 --> 00:03:21.810 align:middle line:84%
It hits my forehead,
and it was so tangible--

00:03:21.810 --> 00:03:23.490 align:middle line:90%
it's so powerful--

00:03:23.490 --> 00:03:25.830 align:middle line:84%
that it pushes me
into the grass.

00:03:25.830 --> 00:03:30.120 align:middle line:84%
Now, I don't know how
long I lay in the grass,

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:32.980 align:middle line:84%
but I ran home to
tell my mother.

00:03:32.980 --> 00:03:34.510 align:middle line:90%
She didn't believe me.

00:03:34.510 --> 00:03:41.470 align:middle line:84%
She thought that I was either
dreaming, fantasizing, lying,

00:03:41.470 --> 00:03:44.750 align:middle line:84%
making it up, but, no,
I wasn't making it up.

00:03:44.750 --> 00:03:45.760 align:middle line:90%
It happened.

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:51.220 align:middle line:84%
And this is why I adhered to
this story through all my life.

00:03:51.220 --> 00:03:52.750 align:middle line:90%
I didn't ebb away from it.

00:03:52.750 --> 00:03:54.100 align:middle line:90%
I wrote about it in my books.

00:03:54.100 --> 00:03:56.290 align:middle line:84%
I talked about it
on documentaries,

00:03:56.290 --> 00:03:59.380 align:middle line:84%
and really, people thought,
come on, this is so far out.

00:03:59.380 --> 00:04:01.580 align:middle line:90%
It can't be true.

00:04:01.580 --> 00:04:05.470 align:middle line:84%
And recently, an Israeli
Air Force officer

00:04:05.470 --> 00:04:09.740 align:middle line:90%
validated this entire scene.

00:04:09.740 --> 00:04:13.480 align:middle line:84%
I was talking about
this amazing encounter--

00:04:13.480 --> 00:04:15.350 align:middle line:90%
I'll call it encounter--

00:04:15.350 --> 00:04:17.720 align:middle line:90%
on a program on the BBC.

00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:20.930 align:middle line:84%
That documentary
was shown in Israel.

00:04:20.930 --> 00:04:25.070 align:middle line:84%
And I get an email from a
man called Jacobi, who says,

00:04:25.070 --> 00:04:27.920 align:middle line:90%
hey, Uri, I was there.

00:04:27.920 --> 00:04:29.000 align:middle line:90%
I saw that sphere.

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:29.880 align:middle line:90%
I saw you.

00:04:29.880 --> 00:04:33.050 align:middle line:84%
I saw a little
boy running home--

00:04:33.050 --> 00:04:35.770 align:middle line:84%
because the apartment building
was very near the garden.

00:04:35.770 --> 00:04:38.810 align:middle line:90%
It was maybe 50 meters away.

00:04:38.810 --> 00:04:42.030 align:middle line:84%
And he actually
validated this story.

00:04:42.030 --> 00:04:42.987 align:middle line:90%
And I said, wow!

00:04:42.987 --> 00:04:43.820 align:middle line:90%
I grabbed the phone.

00:04:43.820 --> 00:04:44.930 align:middle line:90%
I called him.

00:04:44.930 --> 00:04:45.980 align:middle line:90%
I came to Israel.

00:04:45.980 --> 00:04:48.980 align:middle line:84%
I filmed him, and
he says that when

00:04:48.980 --> 00:04:54.420 align:middle line:84%
I ran away from the sphere of
light, the sphere followed me.

00:04:54.420 --> 00:04:59.060 align:middle line:84%
And when I got into our
entrance, into the doorway,

00:04:59.060 --> 00:05:02.930 align:middle line:84%
the sphere exploded on
the facade of our building

00:05:02.930 --> 00:05:07.730 align:middle line:84%
and kind of tarnished
it in a dark residue.

00:05:07.730 --> 00:05:09.170 align:middle line:90%
That was it.

00:05:09.170 --> 00:05:12.500 align:middle line:84%
So there I had a
validation that, no,

00:05:12.500 --> 00:05:14.330 align:middle line:90%
I wasn't making up a story.

00:05:14.330 --> 00:05:17.320 align:middle line:90%
I wasn't dreaming it.

00:05:17.320 --> 00:05:20.830 align:middle line:84%
When I am asked today
what I think that was,

00:05:20.830 --> 00:05:23.150 align:middle line:90%
I have a few theories.

00:05:23.150 --> 00:05:26.380 align:middle line:84%
Let's talk about the
most rational one,

00:05:26.380 --> 00:05:31.450 align:middle line:84%
that it was some kind of
a geophysical phenomena.

00:05:31.450 --> 00:05:38.740 align:middle line:84%
You know, sometimes the earth
releases different gases and--

00:05:38.740 --> 00:05:39.650 align:middle line:90%
who knows?

00:05:39.650 --> 00:05:45.820 align:middle line:84%
But they form bubbles and so--
maybe that was a very simple--

00:05:45.820 --> 00:05:49.450 align:middle line:84%
has a simple
scientific explanation.

00:05:49.450 --> 00:05:57.090 align:middle line:84%
Next theory, that it could have
been a spiritual encounter,

00:05:57.090 --> 00:06:01.800 align:middle line:84%
something to do
with religion maybe,

00:06:01.800 --> 00:06:05.790 align:middle line:84%
something to do with my
belief system, something

00:06:05.790 --> 00:06:09.400 align:middle line:84%
that I created with my
mind, but it was tangible.

00:06:09.400 --> 00:06:10.200 align:middle line:90%
It was there.

00:06:10.200 --> 00:06:12.470 align:middle line:90%
I could touch it.

00:06:12.470 --> 00:06:16.550 align:middle line:84%
The third theory is
the most far-out one--

00:06:16.550 --> 00:06:19.880 align:middle line:84%
that I really had
an alien encounter.

00:06:19.880 --> 00:06:22.160 align:middle line:90%
I did not see an alien being.

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:26.180 align:middle line:84%
I didn't see the grays
with the big eyes.

00:06:26.180 --> 00:06:27.920 align:middle line:90%
I saw this sphere.

00:06:27.920 --> 00:06:31.910 align:middle line:84%
But after I told this
story over and over,

00:06:31.910 --> 00:06:35.060 align:middle line:84%
I get thousands of emails
from people telling me,

00:06:35.060 --> 00:06:38.000 align:middle line:84%
we had the same
encounter, and we

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:41.540 align:middle line:84%
believe it was some kind
of a UFO visitation.

00:06:41.540 --> 00:06:45.440 align:middle line:84%
It was some kind of an
extraterrestrial being trying

00:06:45.440 --> 00:06:47.630 align:middle line:90%
to communicate with us.

00:06:47.630 --> 00:06:49.130 align:middle line:90%
That's a possibility.

00:06:49.130 --> 00:06:51.230 align:middle line:90%
I am a believer.

00:06:51.230 --> 00:06:54.900 align:middle line:84%
There is nothing I
do not believe in.

00:06:54.900 --> 00:06:58.430 align:middle line:84%
I believe in infinity, so
everything is possible.

00:06:58.430 --> 00:07:00.050 align:middle line:90%
Of course, there are UFOs.

00:07:00.050 --> 00:07:03.680 align:middle line:90%
Of course, there are aliens.

00:07:03.680 --> 00:07:09.620 align:middle line:84%
Very soon after this encounter
in this magical Arabic garden,

00:07:09.620 --> 00:07:11.870 align:middle line:90%
I'm eating soup.

00:07:11.870 --> 00:07:16.160 align:middle line:84%
I'm lifting a spoon
up towards my mouth.

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:19.725 align:middle line:84%
Suddenly, the spoon
bends and breaks.

00:07:19.725 --> 00:07:22.470 align:middle line:90%


00:07:22.470 --> 00:07:27.350 align:middle line:84%
And I'm left holding the handle
of the spoon, which maybe I'll

00:07:27.350 --> 00:07:29.430 align:middle line:90%
demonstrate later.

00:07:29.430 --> 00:07:33.150 align:middle line:84%
So my mother looks at me,
and I look at the handle,

00:07:33.150 --> 00:07:38.010 align:middle line:84%
but what does a five and a
half, six-year-old kid know?

00:07:38.010 --> 00:07:41.230 align:middle line:84%
My mother, again,
wasn't surprised.

00:07:41.230 --> 00:07:46.260 align:middle line:84%
And she thought, oh, well, maybe
powers and the paranormal--

00:07:46.260 --> 00:07:49.380 align:middle line:84%
you know, we didn't know
the word paranormal then.

00:07:49.380 --> 00:07:55.710 align:middle line:84%
And then I thought
to myself, hang on--

00:07:55.710 --> 00:07:59.400 align:middle line:90%
spoon-- can I do it again?

00:07:59.400 --> 00:08:00.550 align:middle line:90%
And again?

00:08:00.550 --> 00:08:05.520 align:middle line:84%
So I tried it in
school, and I tried it,

00:08:05.520 --> 00:08:08.280 align:middle line:84%
and I showed it to
my mother's friends.

00:08:08.280 --> 00:08:12.450 align:middle line:84%
Everyone was shocked,
surprised, amazed, aghast,

00:08:12.450 --> 00:08:14.760 align:middle line:90%
to say, what is this?

00:08:14.760 --> 00:08:19.400 align:middle line:84%
That's when I realized that
I had something-- something

00:08:19.400 --> 00:08:21.740 align:middle line:90%
different, something unique.

00:08:21.740 --> 00:08:23.000 align:middle line:90%
My friends in school--

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:25.370 align:middle line:84%
pupils-- they were
good in basketball.

00:08:25.370 --> 00:08:26.840 align:middle line:90%
They were good in soccer.

00:08:26.840 --> 00:08:29.660 align:middle line:90%
They were good in arithmetic.

00:08:29.660 --> 00:08:33.559 align:middle line:84%
I was very average, but
I was good at bending

00:08:33.559 --> 00:08:37.340 align:middle line:90%
spoons and reading minds.

00:08:37.340 --> 00:08:41.450 align:middle line:84%
And the way I discovered
that I could read minds was--

00:08:41.450 --> 00:08:45.450 align:middle line:84%
I was not good in
mathematics, in arithmetic--

00:08:45.450 --> 00:08:49.460 align:middle line:84%
so I could concentrate on
the back of a pupil's head,

00:08:49.460 --> 00:08:51.620 align:middle line:90%
and I would copy the answer.

00:08:51.620 --> 00:08:53.960 align:middle line:84%
The teacher didn't know
how I got the answer

00:08:53.960 --> 00:08:57.680 align:middle line:84%
right when the equation
was wrongly written.

00:08:57.680 --> 00:09:01.490 align:middle line:84%
Then I could look at the
clock on the wall, will it

00:09:01.490 --> 00:09:04.160 align:middle line:90%
to move an hour ahead.

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:07.520 align:middle line:84%
So I started discovering
things that I

00:09:07.520 --> 00:09:09.170 align:middle line:90%
could do at a very early age.

00:09:09.170 --> 00:09:12.120 align:middle line:90%


00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:18.880 align:middle line:84%
Later on in life, I
had to label myself.

00:09:18.880 --> 00:09:22.995 align:middle line:84%
And, of course, I had to
always reinvent myself.

00:09:22.995 --> 00:09:26.560 align:middle line:90%


00:09:26.560 --> 00:09:29.560 align:middle line:90%
And today, I look at it as--

00:09:29.560 --> 00:09:36.040 align:middle line:84%
the phenomena, I see it as
the field of the paranormal.

00:09:36.040 --> 00:09:38.995 align:middle line:84%
There is a section of it
that is mind over matter

00:09:38.995 --> 00:09:44.530 align:middle line:84%
or psychokinesis,
telepathy, the ability

00:09:44.530 --> 00:09:47.520 align:middle line:90%
to do extrasensory perception.

00:09:47.520 --> 00:09:49.747 align:middle line:90%
But I was always controversial.

00:09:49.747 --> 00:09:54.040 align:middle line:90%


00:09:54.040 --> 00:09:56.410 align:middle line:84%
Even in school, even
when I was seven, eight,

00:09:56.410 --> 00:09:59.470 align:middle line:84%
nine-year-old,
children and teachers

00:09:59.470 --> 00:10:05.230 align:middle line:84%
didn't know how to gather--
how to digest this thing.

00:10:05.230 --> 00:10:06.910 align:middle line:90%
Some thought I was a magician.

00:10:06.910 --> 00:10:10.560 align:middle line:84%
Some thought it was just some
kind of a mind over matter

00:10:10.560 --> 00:10:11.360 align:middle line:90%
phenomenon.

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:13.420 align:middle line:90%
Nobody really knew.

00:10:13.420 --> 00:10:20.120 align:middle line:84%
And I realized then
that this is what's

00:10:20.120 --> 00:10:24.920 align:middle line:84%
going to push me out of poverty,
because we were very poor.

00:10:24.920 --> 00:10:26.860 align:middle line:90%
My mother was a seamstress.

00:10:26.860 --> 00:10:28.045 align:middle line:90%
My father was a womanizer.

00:10:28.045 --> 00:10:30.140 align:middle line:90%
He was never at home.

00:10:30.140 --> 00:10:33.310 align:middle line:84%
I remember me and my mom
walking to the flea market.

00:10:33.310 --> 00:10:35.920 align:middle line:84%
She would buy old
American parachutes

00:10:35.920 --> 00:10:38.830 align:middle line:84%
from which she
would sew dresses.

00:10:38.830 --> 00:10:42.010 align:middle line:84%
We would collect
plastic Bakelite spoons

00:10:42.010 --> 00:10:44.680 align:middle line:84%
after people would
eat their ice creams,

00:10:44.680 --> 00:10:47.170 align:middle line:84%
and she would wash
them and resell them.

00:10:47.170 --> 00:10:49.060 align:middle line:90%
We were broke.

00:10:49.060 --> 00:10:56.580 align:middle line:10%
And as I was growing up, I used
my extrasensory perception,

00:10:56.580 --> 00:11:01.890 align:middle line:10%
for instance, to make my
mother win in card games.

00:11:01.890 --> 00:11:04.740 align:middle line:10%
She would take me to
a little card club.

00:11:04.740 --> 00:11:08.730 align:middle line:84%
She would play rummy, and
I would sit next to her.

00:11:08.730 --> 00:11:12.420 align:middle line:10%
And I could look at the
cards of the other players,

00:11:12.420 --> 00:11:14.580 align:middle line:10%
which, obviously, you can't see.

00:11:14.580 --> 00:11:15.960 align:middle line:90%
But I always knew--

00:11:15.960 --> 00:11:20.430 align:middle line:84%
I detected who had the
joker, or who had two jokers.

00:11:20.430 --> 00:11:24.060 align:middle line:84%
And I would kick my
mother's leg to tell her

00:11:24.060 --> 00:11:26.040 align:middle line:90%
which person had the joker.

00:11:26.040 --> 00:11:28.370 align:middle line:84%
In a way, it was
kind of cheating,

00:11:28.370 --> 00:11:30.150 align:middle line:84%
but I could do that
telepathically.

00:11:30.150 --> 00:11:32.430 align:middle line:84%
And my mother would
win quite a lot

00:11:32.430 --> 00:11:36.360 align:middle line:84%
of money, which would help our
existence because she had to--

00:11:36.360 --> 00:11:39.840 align:middle line:84%
she was the earner
in the family.

00:11:39.840 --> 00:11:42.100 align:middle line:90%
My father wasn't around.

00:11:42.100 --> 00:11:45.960 align:middle line:84%
Then my parents
divorced, and my mother

00:11:45.960 --> 00:11:49.680 align:middle line:84%
married a Hungarian Jew
who lived in Cyprus.

00:11:49.680 --> 00:11:52.860 align:middle line:90%
I was 11-- didn't know English.

00:11:52.860 --> 00:11:56.430 align:middle line:84%
So I left Israel, and
suddenly, a whole new culture

00:11:56.430 --> 00:12:00.450 align:middle line:84%
opens up-- different
religions, Turks and Greeks.

00:12:00.450 --> 00:12:03.060 align:middle line:84%
The British also occupied
Cyprus at that time.

00:12:03.060 --> 00:12:05.550 align:middle line:90%
We're talking about 1957.

00:12:05.550 --> 00:12:08.430 align:middle line:84%
And my school was called
Terra Santa College.

00:12:08.430 --> 00:12:11.610 align:middle line:84%
It was up on a hill,
and around the school,

00:12:11.610 --> 00:12:13.980 align:middle line:90%
there were hundreds of caves.

00:12:13.980 --> 00:12:17.700 align:middle line:84%
And we would go down into
the caves to explore.

00:12:17.700 --> 00:12:23.040 align:middle line:84%
And I remember, on a few
occasions, we got lost,

00:12:23.040 --> 00:12:28.560 align:middle line:84%
and I would use my mental
powers to lead the kids out

00:12:28.560 --> 00:12:30.240 align:middle line:90%
of the caves.

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:35.108 align:middle line:84%
So I would use these
abilities in different areas.

00:12:35.108 --> 00:12:36.150 align:middle line:90%
I don't know what it was.

00:12:36.150 --> 00:12:38.220 align:middle line:90%
Maybe it was dowsing.

00:12:38.220 --> 00:12:45.930 align:middle line:84%
Maybe it was using my
extrasensory perception waves,

00:12:45.930 --> 00:12:48.060 align:middle line:90%
almost like a sonar.

00:12:48.060 --> 00:12:54.720 align:middle line:84%
But, yeah, I used to do these
different and unusual things.

00:12:54.720 --> 00:12:58.550 align:middle line:84%
And, again, everybody
was just, wow!

00:12:58.550 --> 00:13:05.100 align:middle line:84%
And I already then felt that I
was entertaining also people.

00:13:05.100 --> 00:13:11.220 align:middle line:84%
Now, my stepfather died a year
