00:13:31.380 --> 00:13:34.220 align:middle line:84%
And there would be
Mossad agents, spies.

00:13:34.220 --> 00:13:36.780 align:middle line:84%
They would check in,
and from there, they

00:13:36.780 --> 00:13:42.120 align:middle line:84%
