00:13:55.540 --> 00:13:56.340 align:middle line:90%
How do you know?

00:13:56.340 --> 00:13:58.530 align:middle line:90%
Why you saying these things?

00:13:58.530 --> 00:14:04.160 align:middle line:84%
To make a long story short,
