far away from our little hotel

00:14:32.660 --> 00:14:34.440 align:middle line:90%
establishment.

00:14:34.440 --> 00:14:36.440 align:middle line:84%
And I realized
that he was spying,

00:14:36.440 --> 00:14:38.810 align:middle line:90%
say, in Egypt or in Syria.

00:14:38.810 --> 00:14:42.470 align:middle line:84%
He would send secret
information in letter forms

00:14:42.470 --> 00:14:43.640 align:middle line:90%
in the envelopes.

00:14:43.640 --> 00:14:48.530 align:middle line:84%
I jumped on the bike and drove
them down to the consulate.

00:14:48.530 --> 00:14:52.040 align:middle line:84%
So I knew that I was
acting for the Mossad.

00:14:52.040 --> 00:14:58.190 align:middle line:84%
And then Yoav says to me, Uri,
I can't understand your powers,

00:14:58.190 --> 00:15:00.350 align:middle line:90%
but you are helping us.

00:15:00.350 --> 00:15:03.580 align:middle line:84%
I want you to go back to
Israel when you're 18,

00:15:03.580 --> 00:15:07.250 align:middle line:84%
join the paratroopers,
go to officer's school,

00:15:07.250 --> 00:15:08.570 align:middle line:90%
and then find me.

00:15:08.570 --> 00:15:10.730 align:middle line:84%
And I told him, Yoav, how
am I going to find you?

00:15:10.730 --> 00:15:13.910 align:middle line:84%
You're going to find me because
we are going to use you.

00:15:13.910 --> 00:15:17.990 align:middle line:10%
You have amazing very special
abilities that we need.

00:15:17.990 --> 00:15:21.850 align:middle line:90%


00:15:21.850 --> 00:15:26.640 align:middle line:84%
I'm asked many times if
I'm unique in my family,

00:15:26.640 --> 00:15:30.300 align:middle line:84%
possessing these abilities,
these skill, these powers--

00:15:30.300 --> 00:15:32.150 align:middle line:90%
call it whatever.

00:15:32.150 --> 00:15:34.270 align:middle line:90%
I'm an only child.

00:15:34.270 --> 00:15:38.250 align:middle line:84%
But having said that, I'm going
to touch on something very

00:15:38.250 --> 00:15:41.280 align:middle line:90%
