00:16:02.790 --> 00:16:06.490 align:middle line:84%
must have my brothers
and sisters, maybe

00:16:06.490 --> 00:16:13.550 align:middle line:84%
an angelic form,
angels, spirits.

00:16:13.550 --> 00:16:16.510 align:middle line:90%
I know I'm not alone.

00:16:16.510 --> 00:16:19.540 align:middle line:84%
That was a shock to me when
