00:16:40.440 --> 00:16:47.520 align:middle line:90%


00:16:47.520 --> 00:16:50.700 align:middle line:84%
Remember I said before
that the secret of success

00:16:50.700 --> 00:16:51.930 align:middle line:90%
is originality.

00:16:51.930 --> 00:16:56.580 align:middle line:84%
And there's nobody who did
spoon bending before me.

00:16:56.580 --> 00:16:58.440 align:middle line:90%
And how did that come about?

00:16:58.440 --> 00:17:03.870 align:middle line:84%
Very interesting-- I was
on a major television

00:17:03.870 --> 00:17:10.450 align:middle line:90%
show on the BBC in 1972.

00:17:10.450 --> 00:17:14.130 align:middle line:84%
It was called the
"David Dimbleby Show."

00:17:14.130 --> 00:17:16.890 align:middle line:84%
And I'll tell you
how it came about.

00:17:16.890 --> 00:17:20.710 align:middle line:84%
I'm sitting-- around me,
skeptical scientists--

00:17:20.710 --> 00:17:24.599 align:middle line:84%
and David Dimbleby
hands me a spoon.

00:17:24.599 --> 00:17:28.850 align:middle line:84%
And he says, show
us your powers!

00:17:28.850 --> 00:17:34.700 align:middle line:84%
And I hold a spoon, and
suddenly, I do something

00:17:34.700 --> 00:17:36.750 align:middle line:90%
that I've never done before.

00:17:36.750 --> 00:17:41.800 align:middle line:84%
I look into the camera, like
this, and I hold up this spoon,

00:17:41.800 --> 00:17:45.470 align:middle line:90%
and I say, everybody at home!

00:17:45.470 --> 00:17:47.510 align:middle line:90%
Go and get your spoons!

00:17:47.510 --> 00:17:52.070 align:middle line:84%
I didn't realize that I sent 10
million people to the kitchen.

00:17:52.070 --> 00:17:54.020 align:middle line:84%
Everybody came back
to the TV screens

00:17:54.020 --> 00:17:57.230 align:middle line:84%
holding a spoon because
no one could fathom--

00:17:57.230 --> 00:18:00.710 align:middle line:84%
believe that spoons are going
to bend in their own homes,

00:18:00.710 --> 00:18:04.400 align:middle line:84%
in the living rooms in
Scotland, in Wales, in England--

00:18:04.400 --> 00:18:08.240 align:middle line:84%
I mean-- and this
is what happened.

00:18:08.240 --> 00:18:11.610 align:middle line:84%
I'm reminding you what
happened on that show.

00:18:11.610 --> 00:18:16.160 align:middle line:84%
I hold a spoon, and I
stroke it very gently.

00:18:16.160 --> 00:18:23.750 align:middle line:84%
And I look at it, and I
say bend, melt, bend, melt,

00:18:23.750 --> 00:18:24.980 align:middle line:90%
and look--

00:18:24.980 --> 00:18:29.540 align:middle line:84%
the metal is becoming
almost like plastic--

00:18:29.540 --> 00:18:32.480 align:middle line:84%
Plastic, see no
heat is produced.

00:18:32.480 --> 00:18:37.390 align:middle line:84%
I say bend, melt,
bend-- and look,

00:18:37.390 --> 00:18:42.145 align:middle line:84%
and then I went like
that, and the spoon broke.

00:18:42.145 --> 00:18:47.350 align:middle line:84%
[ECHOING] Bend, bend,
melt, melt, bend, bend,

00:18:47.350 --> 00:18:53.690 align:middle line:90%
melt, melt, melt.

00:18:53.690 --> 00:18:56.720 align:middle line:84%
Do you know what
happened the instant

00:18:56.720 --> 00:18:59.870 align:middle line:90%
