00:18:59.870 --> 00:19:07.280 align:middle line:84%
The BBC's telephone system
blows up, not because of me,

00:19:07.280 --> 00:19:12.950 align:middle line:84%
not because of my energies,
but because spoons

00:19:12.950 --> 00:19:17.150 align:middle line:90%
were bending in people's homes.

00:19:17.150 --> 00:19:22.550 align:middle line:84%
When the phone calls were
coming in, at that time,

00:19:22.550 --> 00:19:29.480 align:middle line:84%
