calls at the same moment.

00:19:29.480 --> 00:19:34.280 align:middle line:84%
And the phenomena was
huge, not only spoons bend,

00:19:34.280 --> 00:19:37.370 align:middle line:84%
but watches stopped,
watches moved,

00:19:37.370 --> 00:19:41.750 align:middle line:84%
pictures tilted on the
walls, lights flickered.

00:19:41.750 --> 00:19:44.420 align:middle line:84%
This was a mass phenomenon
all over England.

00:19:44.420 --> 00:19:47.750 align:middle line:90%


00:19:47.750 --> 00:19:52.730 align:middle line:84%
The next day, the headlines
screamed, Uri Geller Puts

00:19:52.730 --> 00:19:53.870 align:middle line:90%
England in a Bend.

00:19:53.870 --> 00:19:58.130 align:middle line:90%


00:19:58.130 --> 00:20:03.320 align:middle line:84%
That's when I realized, wow, I
can entertain people and blow

00:20:03.320 --> 00:20:08.180 align:middle line:84%
their minds at the same
time with something, to me,

00:20:08.180 --> 00:20:09.010 align:middle line:90%
is very trivial.

00:20:09.010 --> 00:20:12.170 align:middle line:90%


00:20:12.170 --> 00:20:17.630 align:middle line:84%
When I'm asked, Uri
Geller, are you a magician,

00:20:17.630 --> 00:20:20.000 align:middle line:90%
or are you real?

00:20:20.000 --> 00:20:24.980 align:middle line:90%
And my answer is crystal clear.

00:20:24.980 --> 00:20:29.090 align:middle line:90%
What I do is real.

00:20:29.090 --> 00:20:33.910 align:middle line:84%
And when people ask me,
well, how do you do it?

00:20:33.910 --> 00:20:40.250 align:middle line:84%
I can only explain the process
that goes through my mind.

00:20:40.250 --> 00:20:43.900 align:middle line:90%
Today, I do it--

00:20:43.900 --> 00:20:45.850 align:middle line:90%
if I'm in the mood, I do it.

00:20:45.850 --> 00:20:47.920 align:middle line:90%
I just touch a spoon.

00:20:47.920 --> 00:20:48.760 align:middle line:90%
I think, bend.

00:20:48.760 --> 00:20:51.400 align:middle line:84%
I don't even think
bend any more.

00:20:51.400 --> 00:20:55.360 align:middle line:84%
I visualize it bent, broken,
whatever-- it happens.

00:20:55.360 --> 00:20:57.610 align:middle line:84%
I can talk to
people when I do it.

00:20:57.610 --> 00:21:01.630 align:middle line:84%
When I was young, I would
command the metal to bend.

00:21:01.630 --> 00:21:06.520 align:middle line:84%
I would say bend,
bend, melt, melt.

00:21:06.520 --> 00:21:11.620 align:middle line:84%
Or when I sprout a red radish
seed, I say sprout, sprout.

00:21:11.620 --> 00:21:15.940 align:middle line:84%
So I want to believe
that there is

00:21:15.940 --> 00:21:21.370 align:middle line:84%
a process of some energy
that leaves my mind.

00:21:21.370 --> 00:21:23.890 align:middle line:84%
It has nothing to
do with my finger.

00:21:23.890 --> 00:21:26.260 align:middle line:84%
It has nothing to
do with distance.

00:21:26.260 --> 00:21:27.970 align:middle line:90%
I can do it from afar.

00:21:27.970 --> 00:21:29.920 align:middle line:90%
It takes me more time--

00:21:29.920 --> 00:21:34.050 align:middle line:84%
the thicker the metal,
the more time it takes me.

00:21:34.050 --> 00:21:37.120 align:middle line:84%
These spoons are from
across the coffee shop.

00:21:37.120 --> 00:21:40.190 align:middle line:90%
They are thin, so it's easy.

00:21:40.190 --> 00:21:42.330 align:middle line:90%
There is an energy.

00:21:42.330 --> 00:21:48.370 align:middle line:84%
And let me take
you back to 1924.

00:21:48.370 --> 00:21:53.560 align:middle line:84%
A very, very clever scientist
comes up with a super-amazing

00:21:53.560 --> 00:21:55.510 align:middle line:90%
equation--

00:21:55.510 --> 00:21:58.780 align:middle line:90%
e equals mc square.

00:21:58.780 --> 00:22:02.710 align:middle line:84%
Of course, you all know
that it was Albert Einstein.

00:22:02.710 --> 00:22:06.490 align:middle line:84%
What did it mean by
e equals mc square?

00:22:06.490 --> 00:22:09.880 align:middle line:84%
In very simple terms,
Albert Einstein

00:22:09.880 --> 00:22:16.850 align:middle line:84%
proved scientifically that
everything in the universe

00:22:16.850 --> 00:22:18.770 align:middle line:90%
is made from energy.

00:22:18.770 --> 00:22:24.080 align:middle line:84%
Your energy-- you, you at home,
you are watching the screen--

00:22:24.080 --> 00:22:26.020 align:middle line:90%
your body, your energy.

00:22:26.020 --> 00:22:26.860 align:middle line:90%
I am energy.

00:22:26.860 --> 00:22:27.740 align:middle line:90%
The chair--

00:22:27.740 --> 00:22:28.540 align:middle line:90%
[TAPPING SOUNDS]

00:22:28.540 --> 00:22:30.060 align:middle line:90%
--you hear it?

00:22:30.060 --> 00:22:30.860 align:middle line:90%
It's solid?

00:22:30.860 --> 00:22:33.050 align:middle line:90%
No, it's not solid.

00:22:33.050 --> 00:22:34.250 align:middle line:90%
It's energy.

00:22:34.250 --> 00:22:36.260 align:middle line:90%
The spoon is energy.

00:22:36.260 --> 00:22:38.840 align:middle line:84%
It's vibrating in
such a frequency

00:22:38.840 --> 00:22:43.330 align:middle line:84%
that, to us, it feels
solid, but it's not.

00:22:43.330 --> 00:22:48.280 align:middle line:84%
So when I manipulate a spoon,
when I stroke it gently,

00:22:48.280 --> 00:22:52.990 align:middle line:84%
and when I command it to bend,
or break, or melt, or grow,

00:22:52.990 --> 00:22:57.700 align:middle line:84%
or move, I produce
an energy wave.

00:22:57.700 --> 00:23:00.130 align:middle line:84%
I don't believe it comes
out from my finger.

00:23:00.130 --> 00:23:03.400 align:middle line:84%
I believe it comes
out from my mind,

00:23:03.400 --> 00:23:09.340 align:middle line:84%
and it penetrates the molecular
structure of the metal.

00:23:09.340 --> 00:23:12.955 align:middle line:84%
I've done secret
stuff, for instance,

00:23:12.955 --> 00:23:15.460 align:middle line:84%
at Lawrence Livermore
Radiation Labs, where

00:23:15.460 --> 00:23:17.830 align:middle line:90%
they build nuclear weapons.

00:23:17.830 --> 00:23:20.740 align:middle line:84%
I've done secret experiments
at the American Naval Surface

00:23:20.740 --> 00:23:23.460 align:middle line:84%
Weapons, where they
introduced Nitinol--

00:23:23.460 --> 00:23:26.740 align:middle line:84%
Nitinol-- a metal
that has memory.

00:23:26.740 --> 00:23:30.970 align:middle line:84%
When you bend it physically,
you immerse it in hot water,

00:23:30.970 --> 00:23:34.330 align:middle line:84%
