kind of a universal energy

00:24:11.450 --> 00:24:13.820 align:middle line:90%
from outside me.

00:24:13.820 --> 00:24:17.120 align:middle line:84%
Maybe it has nothing
to do with my mind.

00:24:17.120 --> 00:24:22.020 align:middle line:84%
Maybe there is some kind of
an intelligence above me,

00:24:22.020 --> 00:24:26.960 align:middle line:84%
