00:24:30.890 --> 00:24:32.270 align:middle line:90%
This is so far out.

00:24:32.270 --> 00:24:37.070 align:middle line:84%
This is such a far-out
theory, but it all has to--

00:24:37.070 --> 00:24:41.400 align:middle line:84%
